Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.18,0:01:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Targeted Tailed Beast{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the legendary sandstorm of the Land of Wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd heard rumors, but this is mind-blowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Postponing the Second Exam was wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, one careless move and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:01:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you from Konoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a letter from the Hokage to Kazekage-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll deliver it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Our instructions are to deliver it to him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please let us through?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Second Exam is under the Sand's jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since they won't let us through, should we return to Konoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's really bad acting, you two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to rot in the desert?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get flustered!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kankuro, a Sand proctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You came personally to rescue us, Kankuro-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me. I'll take to you the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't walk… any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of this as part of the Second Exam and get through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Proctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you end up whining over a mere sandstorm, you'll never make it as a Sand chunin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about exceeding one's expectations…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a sandstorm this massive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can barely breathe…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me! I'll cover you.{Original line:"I'll stop it" He doesn't intend to do that, not like he can, anyway}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Gate, Gate of Life… Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop moving around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! But staying still is so stifling…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of getting buried by the sand like this, maybe we should make a run for it…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Byakugan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I broke through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The sandstorm should subside in about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when we'll move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. We just have to endure a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a report on the situation for Kazekage-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You may enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We've received status reports on the sandstorm from the teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nearly all exam participants have been evacuated to the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazekage-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you men blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A Sand Clone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Kazekage-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you thank anyone, it should be Fu of the Hidden Waterfall…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go. The Second Exam will probably resume shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's it coming from…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We chose the wrong route.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't see what's happening on higher ground from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That sound gives me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We should high tail it out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but let's proceed with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Power of Dharma: Silhouette.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The tempo's changed. Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The shadows…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1\fad(300,200)}(Suna Bunshin!: Sand Clone!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Suna Bunshin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara-sama, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Their target is me. There's no need for you to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our duty as Sand Shinobi to fight when our Kazekage is threatened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to the Second Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That is your duty as Sand Shinobi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,, {\an8\i1\fad(300,200)} Hōriki Fūinjutsu, Sen no Rikyu: Dharma Sealing Jutsu, Hermit Removing Separation Absorption   ){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dharma Sealing Jutsu:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sen no Rikyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm losing my power…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's pull out the chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! I can do this alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I order you as the Kazekage to withdraw immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And not a word of this to anyone, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the central tower and get help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kazekage-sama swore us to secrecy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! His life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Resistance is useless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the sealing jutsu passed on{\i0} {\i1}to me by Priest Bunpuku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, I can extract Shukaku{\i0} {\i1}from Gaara.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukata! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuri! Yukata can't go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikoshi, take care of Yukata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to inform headquarters about Gaara-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But, by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuri…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'm going to make a hundred friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She is so impulsive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's abandoning the Chunin Exams? What is she up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fu…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going, Foo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going back for the Second Exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I just can't figure her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The friend I just made is in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're going to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, Fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind the Second Exam already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to get her back safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let us pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:14:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a letter for Kazekage-sama from the Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We must deliver it directly to Kazekage-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I explained that's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah… Kazekage-sama isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world? The Kazekage....?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This chain… is extracting my chakra…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no mistake.{\i0} {\i1}That's Bijū chakra!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If left alone, his Bijūt{\i0} {\i1}will be extracted, and he'll die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away! This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It does have something to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You're a Jinchuriki too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can feel your pain too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you taught me that friends understand each other's pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sucking out my power…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So there's another one…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How interesting…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not even Bunpuku-sama ever{\i0} {\i1}sealed two Bijū at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the perfect opportunity to test{\i0} {\i1}the power of the Hōriki Fūin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fu! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I failed…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hōriki, Sen no Rikyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If the sandstorm continued any longer, this would have become our grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know what will happen next. That's the Demon Desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this Second Exam over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! The central tower isn't far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something we need to do before we head for the central tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone I want to settle things with too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have someone like that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something the matter with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We have two scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both "Heaven" scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you keep something so important a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't intend to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that things happened and I didn't have a chance to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a really bad excuse…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll just have to recoup and obtain an "Earth" scroll somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Byakugan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Over that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! You're going to take a scroll from someone who's ready to drop from exhaustion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do something so cowardly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't jump to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't ignore someone in distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Neji would never stoop to such a dirty trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not! The thought never crossed my mind…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kazekage-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is attacking Gaara-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a little longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will come to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative thoughts aren't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.22,0:22:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how long we wait, reinforcements from the Sand won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Again with those negative thoughts!
Comment: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you still say that if you knew
Comment: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that the one attacking us is from the Sand?
Comment: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Naruto Shippuden: "Neji's Judgment"
Comment: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure someone will come to save us!
Comment: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,IN NARUTO'S FOOTSTEPS ~ THE PATH TRAVELED NEJI'S JUDGMENT
